====Usage notes====
* As [[Sol]] is the name of our star, this phrase is usually used to refer specifically to our own sun and planets (the Sol system), in which case it is used with ''the'' and generally capitalised (as '''the Solar system''' or '''the Solar System'''). Other systems are then known as [[star system]]s or [[planetary system]]s, or specified by the name of the individual star (the [[Alpha Centauri]] system).

